Modifications made by Starks.Design:

  - Namespace: HTML attribute prefix `fs-` renamed to `data-sd-`
  - Global: `window.FinsweetAttributes` renamed to `window.SDA`
  - Type identifiers: `FinsweetAttribute*` renamed to `SDA*` / `SDAttributeKey`
  - Package names: `@finsweet/attributes-*` renamed to `@starks-design/sda-*`
  - Scope: reduced to `list` and `utils` packages (other modules removed)
  - Branding: documentation, README, metadata adjusted for Starks.Design
  - Auto-rebrand script: `scripts/rebrand.py` documents all transformations

